    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Priopoda macrophyae sp. nov., female (holotype) and male (paratype)—A: head, lateral view; B: mandible and malar space, postero-lateral view; C: areolet of right fore wing; D: hind tarsal claw; E: propodeum, dorsal view; F: apex of metasoma, ventro-lateral view; G: posterior margin of subgenital plate; H: apex of metasoma, lateral view." ;
